asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

description: Ziggy Flufdust is an androgynous, alien rock star who came to The Underground before an impending apocalyptic disaster known simply as "the wreck" to deliver a message of hope. Ziggy is an over the top, sexually liberated rock star and serves as a commentary for the sections of Fluf society in which celebrities are worshipped. After accumulating a large following of fans and being lauded as a messiah, Ziggy eventually fell victim to his own fame and excessive success. Following this fall from superstardom, he was able to transcend to the level beneath The Underground to the dance floor of legend. He now performs regularly with DJ LuciFur and Screamin Jay Flufkins, an event not to be missed should you ever get the chance.

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle.

name: Beacon
description: Have you ever wished you had someone that would always seem to be there when you needed them the most? I hope I can be that for you one day. I have been blessed with bright yellowy green fur that is believed to be genetically engineered with fire fly and phosphorescence, so our fur has a gorgeous glow in the dark. It seems to charge during the day so is super bright up until around midnight, then it starts fading until sunrise. A dose of mycelium will also give it a huge boost and the aura emanating has this magical effect seemingly to ward off danger. I also tend to start glowing if danger is approaching. Its super handy throughout the night or in stressful situations as it also has a calming effect. During the days after the wreck we were able to guide fluf in the dark safely through the tunnels or away from danger and provide a warm sense of safety with our light. They call us Beacons, and I have been blessed with the name for dedicating my life to always be there for fluf in times of need. My Hi vis jacket has cool reflectors on it so you can spot me even easier. I always try to carry a supply of mycelium with me to help fluf who have anxiety or depression. Anxiety is worrying about the future, and depression is worrying about the past. I help people become more present and connect with the now. Micro doses have helped so many people, and macro doses, well, I will let you experience that yourself one day and can be your guide. I will be there partying with you, having deep and meaningfuls with you, laughing with you, crying with you, and there to support you through the curve **** life throws. But MOST of all, I will be there wybing with you making sure you are grateful for this life, for being here, right at this very moment, in this miracle.

This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

**Official Collections:**

[FLUF World: Thingies](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-thingies)

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)

[FLUF World: Scenes & Sounds](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-scenes-and-sounds)

asset_contract.name: FLUF
asset_contract.description:
This is FLUF World…

A metaverse ecosystem of NFT character collectables and a global, creative community. From our genesis collection Flufs, to Thingies, Party Bears and more to come, we’re building a world that’s yours to shape, explore and call home. 

Flufs are the collection that started it all. 10,000 3D rabbit avatars, programmatically-generated from over 270 traits! Unique by at least three degrees of separation, Flufs are yours to trade, collect and customise through our growing Scenes & Sounds collection. 

But Flufs aren’t just furry faces... Metaverse-ready and full of surprises, they’re your ticket to a world of exclusive content, digital connectivity, IRL experiences and more.

Welcome to the Fluffle. 

---

[FLUF World: Burrows](https://opensea.io/collection/fluf-world-burrows)
